There were 2 other sightings in Parker on or around January 14th 2012
divs: sighting detailsat that point, i saw another one (or maybe the same one) off to the north about 1\2 half mile from where i saw the first one. this one was very bright, lower in altitude, and sliding west above the park to our nw. i yelled at my wife to come out side. we both watched it for several minutes. i grabbed the camera, but at this point, it was starting to ascend. it was identical to the first one that i saw. that's four sightings in two days. what gives? i'm not aware of any time lost.
Summary: After first sighting, this one showed from the North. My wife and I watched it for several minutes
